						<div class="postbody">You forgot to initialize/disable the sprites, so they're all appearing at the upper-left corner of the screen.
<br />
<br />Also, there are probably a few other problems in that program (which would prevent it from working on an NES), but I'll leave those for somebody else to describe in detail.</div>

					
